dct_title_s: Tunesien 1:50,000 : Deutsche Heereskarte / herausgegeben vom OKH/Gen. S.d.H., Chef des Kriegskarten- und Vermessungswesens.
dct_description_sm: Relief shown by contours, shading, and spot heights. Depths shown by contours and soundings. In upper margin: Nicht für die Öffentlichkeit bestimmt! Sheets separately numbered and subtitled in upper margin, e.g.: I 32 SO 2/01/02--Djerba. Includes notes, compilation diagrams, boundary and sheet diagrams, and index to adjoining sheets. Includes French - German abbreviation list  and Arabic  abbreviations translated  to French and German.
dct_creator_sm: Germany. Heer. Generalstab. Chef des Kriegskarten- und Vermessungswesens
